query: SELECT dusun from kartu_ibu_registration where userID='user12' group by dusun

SELECT kartu_ibu_registration.dusun, count(*) as kunjungan_bulan_lalu1 FROM kohort_bayi_balita_kunjungan inner join kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan on kohort_bayi_balita_kunjungan.childid = kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.childid INNER JOIN kartu_anc_registration ON kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.motherid = kartu_anc_registration.motherid INNER JOIN kartu_ibu_registration ON kartu_anc_registration.kiid = kartu_ibu_registration.kiid where kartu_ibu_registration.userid =  'user12' and kohort_bayi_balita_kunjungan.tanggalKunjunganBayiPerbulan IN ((SELECT DATEDIFF( 2015-12-16,kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.tanggallahiranak ) AS DATE FROM kohort_bayi_balita_kunjungan INNER JOIN kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan ON kohort_bayi_balita_kunjungan.childid = kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.childid)) >= '12' or  kohort_bayi_balita_kunjungan.tanggalKunjunganBayiPerbulan IN ((SELECT DATEDIFF( 2015-12-16,kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.tanggallahiranak ) AS DATE FROM kohort_bayi_balita_kunjungan INNER JOIN kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan ON kohort_bayi_balita_kunjungan.childid = kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.childid)) <= '23' AND kohort_bayi_balita_kunjungan.beratBadanBayiSetiapKunjunganBayiPerbulan IN (select count(*) from kohort_bayi_balita_kunjungan inner join kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan on kohort_bayi_balita_kunjungan.childid = kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.childid INNER JOIN kartu_anc_registration ON kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.motherid = kartu_anc_registration.motherid where kohort_bayi_balita_kunjungan.beratBadanBayiSetiapKunjunganBayiPerbulan !='') >=8 AND kohort_bayi_balita_kunjungan.clientVersionSubmissionDate BETWEEN  '2015-01-01' AND  '2015-11-31' group by kartu_ibu_registration.dusun
